Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.85,0:00:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.04,0:00:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,真心不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.46,0:00:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,昴  你怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.86,0:00:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此  這就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.52,0:00:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,別過來  快跑  快…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.17,0:00:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,納豆還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.83,0:00:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,等著我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.56,0:00:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,一共363日元
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.77,0:00:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,齒邊10元
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.80,0:01:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.08,0:01:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,一定會…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.67,0:01:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,救你的
Comment: 0,0:01:21.15,0:01:21.15,Comment,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.87,0:01:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟一整天窩在家裡玩遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.93,0:01:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,眼睛肯定也累了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:01:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.70,0:02:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎麼看都不像是人造假貨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.43,0:02:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.13,0:02:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.41,0:02:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,難道這就是所謂的異世界召喚嗎!?
